    .sponsorship.container
      h2.text-center PyCon CZ 2015 Sponsorship
      .row
        p #[a(href="/", ) PyCon Czech Republic] is a two-day conference organized by the Python community for the Python community. The conference will include 1 full day of talks featuring 2 international keynote speakers (all sessions will be held in English), and 1 day of sprints and workshops where Pythonistas can get together and work on their open source projects.
        p This year is the first edition of PyCon CZ, and we look forward to bringing the tradition of diverse and insightful speakers, top-quality venues, and a great atmosphere to Czech Republic. Regional PyCons are well-known for attracting developers, sysadmins, writers, designers, and community members from all over.
        p These packages are recommendations for your company or organization. If you would like to contribute a different amount or alternative sponsorship format, please let us know and we’ll be happy to discuss custom packages.

      .row
        h3.text-left Platinum (€3,000) (Limit 1)
        p As a Platinum sponsor, you will receive the following benefits:
        ul.text-left
          li Full width logo on the event website
          li Three (3) tickets
          li Display unlimited promotional (“Swag”) items
          li Address audience during a sponsorship lightning talk (5 minutes)
          li Space for copy in welcome/goodbye emails to attendees

      .row
        h3.text-left Gold (€1,500) (Limit 4)
        p As a Gold sponsor, you will receive the following benefits:
        ul.text-left
          li Large logo on the event website
          li Two (2) tickets
          li Physical logo at the event (eg. banners, badge, stickers, etc)
          li Sponsorship branding, one of the following
            ul
              li Name the lunch (limit 2)
              li Name the pre-registration social (limit 1)
              li Name the main conference party (limit 1)
              li Lanyards (limit 1)

      .row
        h3.text-left Silver (€750) (Limit 4)
        p As a Silver sponsor, you will receive the following benefits:
        ul.text-left
          li One (1) ticket
          li Small logo on the event website
          li Display 1 promotional (“Swag”) item

      .row.text-left
        h4 Inquiries
        Please direct all inquiries to <strong>Tomáš Ehrlich</strong> at #[a(href="mailto:tomas.ehrlich@gmail.com", ) tomas.ehrlich@gmail.com]






